          <lg n="1">
            <l xml:id="swift-400-59L2-line-1" n="1"><hi rend="display-initial">T</hi>HE Sage who said he should be proud</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-400-59L2-line-2" n="2">Of Windows in his Breast,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-400-59L2-line-3" n="3">Because he ne'er one Thought allowed,</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-400-59L2-line-4" n="4">That might not be confess'd.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-400-59L2-line-5" n="5"><lb/>His Window scrawled by ev'ry Rake,</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-400-59L2-line-6" n="6">His Breast again would cover;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-400-59L2-line-7" n="7">And fairly bid the D──l take</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-400-59L2-line-8" n="8">The Diamond and the Lover.</l>
          </lg>
